ttr-left\">Features:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">COMPACT SLUICE GOLD PANNING KIT: Included gold recovery tools; ASR Outdoor dual riffle pans, heavy duty sand scoop and mini sluice box, cleaning and storage equipment, gold snifter bottle, glass vials and magnifying tweezers, this gold panning kit has all the equipment needed for a successful day of gold panning in the field</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">PORTABLE MINI SLUICE BOX: Measuring 12 inches, ready to use out of the box with no tools or assembly required; the mini sluice box is made from durable and weatherproof aluminum, comes with V-shaped ribbed rubber matting, making it ideal for fine gold recovery</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">MULTIPURPOSE DRAWSTRING BACKPACK: This gold panning or gold prospecting kit conveniently houses all the included gold mining equipment in a multipurpose black drawstring backpack, making this kit easily portable, organized and convenient to tote to and from your field site</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">GOLD CLEANING AND STORAGE TOOLS: In addition to the recovery equipment included in this kit, you also have a great assortment of useful tools to help you clean and store gold, gems or other found minerals; for cleaning, the gold snifter bottle and pipettes; for storage, the glass vials, and for examination, the magnifying tweezers</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">GOLD PANNING KIT INCLUDES: This compact, lightweight, portable gold prospecting kit includes 10 inch and 12 inch dual riffle pans, prospectors sand scoop, black sand magnet tool, tweezers, gold snifter bottle&nbsp;and pipettes, glass vials, 12\" mini sluice box, a 30 holes/inch classifier and drawstring backpack</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>ASR Outdoor Lightweight Backpack Gold Panning Kit with Mini Aluminum Sluice Box, 14pc</h1>\n\t\t\t<p>Gold panning and recovery equipment prospectors kit designed to be lightweight and easily carried into your claim site to evaluate your gold prospect before taking in bigger equipment. This 14pc compact, portable and travel friendly gold prospecting kit has it all, allowing you to focus on panning and recovery, while we take care of the rest.\n\nThis kit includes: 10\" riffled gold pan and 12\" dual riffle pan, one prospecting sand scoop, a 8lb black sand magnetic separator tool, magnifying tweezers, glass collection vials, pocket 12\" mini gold sluice box, a gold snuffer bottle and pipettes,  30 holes/inch mini classifier screen and black drawstring backpack.\n\nThe highlight of this kit is without a doubt the mini sluice box. Measuring 12 inches, the mini aluminum sluice box for gold recovery from ASR Outdoor is ready to use out of the box with no assembly required, is constructed from durable and weatherproof aluminum and comes with V-shaped ribbed rubber sluice matting, making it ideal for fine gold recovery. The removable mesh screen allows for adding a layer of woven vinyl miners moss to the sluice box if desired. This kit is easy to carry and extremely portable as it comes with a drawstring backpack to hold all the included gold mining equipment, keeping everything organized and convenient to tote to and from the field site.\n\nLightweight, compact and convenient, this ASR Outdoor 14 piece portable gold panning kit has you covered from start to finish on the gold prospecting front; setting you up for success in the field whether you’re panning, cleaning, sorting, examining or storing.\n\nGood luck and happy gold prospecting on your mining claim, we hope you strike it rich!</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t<p>© 2026</p></div></div><div style=\"clear:both\"><table></table></div>",
